# Advanced Scientific Calculator (Java)

A modern **Scientific Calculator Desktop Application** built using **Java Swing**.  
The calculator supports advanced mathematical operations including graph plotting, matrix calculations, equation solving, and expression parsing.

## Features

- Basic arithmetic operations (+, -, *, /)
- Scientific functions (sin, cos, tan, log, sqrt)
- Expression parser
- Graph plotting for mathematical functions
- Matrix calculator
- Quadratic equation solver
- Calculation history panel

## Technologies Used

- Java
- Java Swing (GUI)
- Java Math Library

